Notes: With the score tied at 37, Missouri Western goes on a 11-0 run to take the
lead for good...UMR gets to within five on two occasions, the latest at 58-53
with 1:26 to go before Western scores the final four points...The Griffons hit
seven of their 11 3-pt. baskets in the second half.
